              ["Stomach", "• Peptic Ulcer Disease\n• Erosive Gastritis\n• Gastric Neoplasm"],
              ["Duodenum", "• Peptic Ulcer Disease\n• Diverticula\n• Vascular anomalies (Angiodysplasia)"]
            ]
          },
